{"tid":1122502,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"椰汁咖喱","createTime":"2019-04-24T03:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T03:47:03.000Z","uid":37325,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"940a16670f969d01def971a30b74bfb624a0e604","tid":1122502,"uid":37325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:47:03.000Z","msg":"今日無野做落樓買料整椰汁咖喱<br />\n平時都係炒下粉麵飯 整咖喱都係第一次<br />\n我以我所唸既方法去做 <br />\n<br />\n材料有:<br />\n佳之選垃圾雞扒 三細塊<br />\n紅蘿蔔               一棵<br />\n薯仔                  兩個(買多左)<br />\n洋蔥                  一個<br />\n椰漿<br />\n雞湯<br />\n咖喱粉<br />\n<br />\n首先將急凍雞扒浸鹽水溶雪 然後切柳再用鹽+少少糖+胡椒粉+生粉醃一醃佢<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xrxod8y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxrxod8y.jpg&h=49b009eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅蘿蔔薯仔洋蔥切粒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lk589G3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLk589G3.jpg&h=ecbccf16&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n煎下D雞柳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vokpH2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvokpH2b.jpg&h=d616d173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炒完洋蔥再落紅蘿蔔薯仔一齊炒<br />\n之後落咖喱粉炒多下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gENFPd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gENFPd.jpg&h=f52f821e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再落埋雞柳<br />\n落雞湯煲一個字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUu9T9u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUu9T9u.jpg&h=f1554855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落埋椰漿再煲多一陣打個茨熄火上碟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktaw7uC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fktaw7uC.jpg&h=1ff1abcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果同理想有D分別 咖喱粉落得太多有D辣<br />\n椰漿應該最後熄火落<br />\n大約800mL雞湯落成罐165mL椰漿都好似無咩椰味<br />\n唔知關唔關煲多一陣事"}]}